data.text:
Star Crew: Nani, Samantha, Krishnudu

Director: Gautham Menon

Producer: Venkat Somasundaram, Reshma Gatala, Gautham Menon

Music Director: Ilaiyaraaja

Movie Description: Yeto Vellipoyindhi Manasu is a forthcoming Telugu romance film written & directed by Gautham Menon, featuring Nani & Samantha in the lead roles. The film, featuring film score and soundtrack composed by Ilaiyaraaja & cinematography by M. S. Prabhu, is also being simultaneously shot in Tamil and Hindi as Neethaane En Ponvasantham with actor Jiiva & Assi Nabbe Poorey Sau with actor Aditya Roy Kapur.
